<FILEID>AP-NR-10-25-88 1233EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>u p AM-NetworkProjections Bjt   10-25 0905</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Network Projections, Bjt,870</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Western Voters Feel Robbed When TV Projects Winners Early</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Retransmitting a0561 to fix keyword line, making it conform
to AMs Digest.</NOTE>
